				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {WS}_2$$\end{document} such radius is around 40Å56, i.e. once more about 10 lattice constants.

